title: [Courtyard, Rose Garden]
description: A colorful variety of roses surround the tiled pathway that leads to the central gazebo.  A few honeybees dart in and out of the petals, unbothered by the multitude of folks enjoying the warm sun.

A colorful variety of roses surround the tiled pathway that leads to the central gazebo.  Several fireflies hover over the plants, their illumination providing an evening light show for the courtyard's guests.
